LEGAL_PUBLIC.PRIVACY_S7_BODY:
Barnabi uses cookies and similar technologies for:

• Authentication — keeping you logged in across sessions;
• Session management — maintaining your preferences and state;
• Analytics — understanding aggregate usage patterns to improve the Platform.

You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may limit certain features such as staying logged in. We do not serve behavioural advertising cookies.

LEGAL_PUBLIC.PRIVACY_S9_BODY:
Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:

• Access — request a copy of the personal data we hold about you;
• Correction — ask us to correct inaccurate or incomplete data;
• Deletion — request that we delete your personal data, subject to legal retention requirements;
• Portability — receive your data in a structured, machine-readable format;
• Objection or restriction — object to or ask us to restrict certain types of processing;
• Withdraw consent — where processing is based on consent, withdraw it at any time without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing.

To exercise these rights, use in-app support or the settings in your account.
